     "text": [
      "✓ Filtered: 113 pipelines\n",
      "Loading Oil-NGL geometries (113 unique route files for 113 rows)...\n",
      "  50/113 (44%) | elapsed 0.1s | last=P5376\n",
      "  75/113 (66%) | elapsed 0.1s | last=P6062\n",
      "  100/113 (88%) | elapsed 0.2s | last=P6149\n",
      "  113/113 (100%) | elapsed 0.2s | last=P7981\n",
      "  ✓ Loaded: 84/113 unique files | Missing/failed: 29\n",
      "  Failed samples: P5335: empty geometry; P5343: empty geometry; P5344: empty geometry; P5345: empty geometry; P5346: empty geometry; P5347: empty geometry; P5348: empty geometry; P5354: empty geometry; P5367: empty geometry; P5370: empty geometry ...\n",
      "✓ Export ready: 113 pipelines, 51 columns\n"
